---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services | Cascade Creatives" active="services">

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label animate-in">Services</p>
    <h1 class="animate-in delay-1">Design. Content. <em>Strategy.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub animate-in delay-2">Everything your business needs to show up better online &mdash; from the website itself, to the content on it, to the strategy behind it.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">01 &mdash; Primary</p>
    <h2>Web Design &amp; <em>Development</em></h2>
    <p>Custom websites built on modern frameworks &mdash; fast, clean, and designed to convert. We design and build websites from scratch using Astro, static HTML, and Webflow &mdash; depending on what fits. Every site is custom-designed, performance-optimized, and built with SEO fundamentals baked in.</p>
    <p>We also redesign and rebuild existing sites that have fallen behind &mdash; fixing what&rsquo;s broken, rewriting copy, restructuring content, and modernizing the experience.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What&rsquo;s Included:</strong> <span>Custom design &middot; Responsive development &middot; SEO &amp; performance &middot; Copy guidance &middot; Content integration &middot; Hosting setup &middot; Post-launch support</span></p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Web Project &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">02 &mdash; Integrated</p>
    <h2>Content <em>Production</em></h2>
    <p>A website is only as good as what&rsquo;s on it. We produce professional video, photography, and aerial drone content &mdash; formatted for your site, social media, and paid ads. This isn&rsquo;t a separate service bolted on &mdash; it&rsquo;s integrated into the same engagement.</p>
    <p>Our production team has over a decade of experience &mdash; commercials, brand films, real estate tours, event coverage, and social content. FAA Part 107 licensed for drone work.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What We Produce:</strong> <span>Brand video &middot; Social reels &amp; ads &middot; Product/service photography &middot; Aerial drone coverage &middot; Event coverage &middot; Remote editing &middot; Multi-format delivery</span></p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Shoot &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">03 &mdash; Strategic</p>
    <h2>AI &amp; Digital <em>Strategy</em></h2>
    <p>AI is changing how businesses create content, build websites, and operate online. We help companies understand what&rsquo;s actually useful &mdash; and implement it. Not hype, not theory. Practical AI integration into real workflows.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What This Looks Like:</strong> <span>AI workflow audit &middot; Content automation setup &middot; Digital presence review &middot; Tool recommendations &middot; Website strategy &middot; Growth roadmap</span></p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Let&rsquo;s Talk Strategy &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="cta-section reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Not sure what you <em>need?</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Tell us what you&rsquo;re working on and we&rsquo;ll recommend the right approach.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
